WHITE SPOT VIRUS, SHRIMP - ECUADOR
************************************
A ProMED post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Shrimp, "white spot" disease - USA (Texas) 980420214349
Shrimp viruses, breeding stock import ban - Peru 990710204103
Shrimp virus 950628
